        "Title": "The arms trifecta",
        "Location": "LOCATION_PARIS",
        "PublicId": "102746723752",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Paris/_scene_paris.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 335ce4e7-36bb-45cd-aa24-18564d48ed4e).Image",
        "Description": "We&apos;ve tracked down the top arms dealers of a global syndicate to Paris where they are using the silent auction to sell their weapons to the highest bidders. Take care of them by using the same weapons they are selling.  While you&apos;re at it, take care of their top lieutenants by making it look like an accident. Good luck.",
